title: PSO2 Episode Oracle Pack
description: Get in-game items exclusive to Phantasy Star Online 2 through this pack. Purchase this pack to obtain "Phantasy Star Online 2 Episode Oracle" avatar items and other items that will give you an edge on your PSO2 adventures.
longDescription:
Get in-game items exclusive to Phantasy Star Online 2 through this pack.  Purchase this pack to obtain "Phantasy Star Online 2 Episode Oracle" avatar items and other items that will give you an edge on your PSO2 adventures.

# The following items are included in this pack:
 - ARKS Badge: Green ×10
 - EX Triboost +200% ×1

Note: The character in the image may have some items that are not included in the pack.

The items obtainable through this content are exclusive to Phantasy Star Online 2. These items cannot be used in other services, including the Japanese service.

After purchase, you will receive the content the next time you log in to Phantasy Star Online 2. Receive the items via [Visiphone] -> [Receive Campaign Items] -> [Purchase / Receive Benefits].

Phantasy Star Online 2 is required in order to use this content. Please update to the latest patch before using this content.

ARKS Badge: Green can be exchanged for any item displayed at the "Badge Exchange Shop" in the game. The costume shown in the image cannot be obtained directly. It can be exchanged for in the game with  "ARKS Badge: Green".

It may take up to 24 hours for the product to be reflected upon your first billed purchase. If over 48 hours have passed and the product has still not been reflected, please contact us through the Phantasy Star Online 2 Official Website.
